{
  "stem": "7683.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But regardless, we did it because we had to survive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because the food in the camp was so bad that nobody could really survive off it, and a lot of people died in a very short time.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had, in the morning, black water what's supposed to be coffee.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then in afternoon, we got a slice of bread about an inch wide and a so-called soup.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now we called it 'spit soup.' It was a soup [INAUDIBLE], the corn with the skin, with everything so you had to spit it out.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some people didn't eat it, and they really died [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that was the only food what you got to eat, so you had to steal all this food.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I don't think we talked about home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We talk about the situation where we are in, and talk a lot-- they kept you so busy, you always had so much happening every minute of every day of it, so you really very seldom talk about the life in normal before you came to the camp.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was a long time was talking about uprising.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But well, first of all, was a very secret thing, because people talk sometimes, and it comes quick out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if it comes out, even a suspicion, it would killed us all.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there was no talk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was really not originally involved in it because I worked with Selma, who was Dutch.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And even not all the Polish ones were involved in it because, as I say, it was a big secret.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I had friends which were inside, and I was always up what's going on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I didn't have any assignments, because the assignments of the uprising was that people on the work will kill some of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
